videos.headline: UCF's Aaron Robinson exits game on a stretcher
videos.description: UCF DB Aaron Robinson takes a hard hit on the opening kickoff and would remain on the ground before being taken off on a stretcher.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UCF’s Aaron Robinson exits game on a stretcher) 2018/08/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Milton finds Nixon for 34-yard TD
videos.description: UCF QB McKenzie Milton lobs a 34-yard pass into the end zone to WR Tre Nixon for the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Milton finds Nixon for 34-yard TD) 2018/08/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Milton to Nixon to put UCF up 42-10
videos.description: UCF quarterback McKenzie Milton extends Golden Knights' blowout of UConn with a 11-yard touchdown pass to wide receiver Tre Nixon.

videos.headline: UCF RB converts 4th down into touchdown
videos.description: Greg McCrae catches 4th-and-2 pass and converts it into a 36-yard touchdown for UCF.
